<i>You must have received your free ticket.
Oh, I'm so glad.</i>

888
01:04:30,560 --> 01:04:33,643
Ladies and gentlemen,
children of all ages,

889
01:04:33,800 --> 01:04:36,883
I give you the average man.

890
01:04:38,960 --> 01:04:40,724
Impressive, eh?

891
01:04:44,640 --> 01:04:47,450
Ooh!

892
01:05:02,640 --> 01:05:03,721
Jim.

893
01:05:03,920 --> 01:05:05,809
Jim, are you still...

894
01:05:06,320 --> 01:05:08,846
Oh, God. Oh, God.

895
01:05:10,840 --> 01:05:13,127
It's okay, let it come.

896
01:05:14,400 --> 01:05:17,927
He showed me pictures of my daughter.
Have you seen her?

897
01:05:18,840 --> 01:05:20,251
Yes, she's alive.

898
01:05:20,400 --> 01:05:21,526
And?

899
01:05:21,680 --> 01:05:23,444
The police are right behind me.

900
01:05:23,600 --> 01:05:24,761
I'll stay with you, until...

901
01:05:24,920 --> 01:05:27,287
No, I'll survive.

902
01:05:27,960 --> 01:05:31,567
Go after him. I want him brought in.

903
01:05:31,720 --> 01:05:33,722
And I want it done by the book.

904
01:05:37,480 --> 01:05:39,164
By the book!

905
01:05:39,320 --> 01:05:40,924
You have to!

906
01:05:41,400 --> 01:05:44,529
We have to show him our way works.

907
01:05:54,880 --> 01:05:56,882
<i>JOKER". Let me ask you something.</i>

908
01:05:57,040 --> 01:06:01,489
<i>What does it matter if you send me back to
the asylum if it doesn't matter to me?</i>

909
01:06:03,720 --> 01:06:05,290
I've proved my point.

910
01:06:05,480 --> 01:06:07,209
Gordon's been driven mad.

911
01:06:07,400 --> 01:06:12,122
<i>I've demonstrated there's no difference
between me and everyone else.</i>

912
01:06:13,400 --> 01:06:17,041
<i>All it takes is one bad day.</i>

913
01:06:17,240 --> 01:06:19,561
<i>That's how far the world
is from where I am,</i>

914
01:06:19,720 --> 01:06:21,802
just one bad day.

915
01:06:22,880 --> 01:06:24,484
<i>You had a bad day once, am I right?</i>

916
01:06:24,640 --> 01:06:26,927
<i>Oh, I know I am.</i>

917
01:06:27,080 --> 01:06:28,161
<i>I can tell.</i>

918
01:06:28,320 --> 01:06:31,164
<i>You had a bad day and everything changed.</i>

919
01:06:31,400 --> 01:06:34,643
<i>Dressing up like a flying rat
doesn't hide it, it screams it.</i>

920
01:06:34,840 --> 01:06:37,366
<i>You had a bad day
and it drove you as crazy</i>

921
01:06:37,520 --> 01:06:40,683
