922
01:06:40,840 --> 01:06:42,056
<i>GROANS}
- You have to keep pretending</i>

923
01:06:42,080 --> 01:06:43,206
<i>that life makes sense,</i>

924
01:06:43,360 --> 01:06:45,806
<i>that there's some point
to all this struggling.</i>

925
01:06:45,960 --> 01:06:48,088
<i>You make me want to puke.</i>

926
01:06:54,280 --> 01:06:56,442
Shh.

927
01:06:57,920 --> 01:07:00,321
<i>I mean, what is it with you?</i>

928
01:07:00,480 --> 01:07:03,131
<i>What made you what you are?</i>

929
01:07:03,760 --> 01:07:06,240
<i>Girlfriend killed by the mob, maybe?</i>

930
01:07:06,400 --> 01:07:08,323
<i>Brother carved up by some mugger?</i>

931
01:07:08,480 --> 01:07:10,244
<i>Something like that, I know.</i>

932
01:07:10,400 --> 01:07:13,643
<i>Because something like that
happened to me.</i>

933
01:07:19,560 --> 01:07:23,485
<i>Sometimes, I remember it one way,
sometimes another.</i>

934
01:07:24,040 --> 01:07:25,883
<i>If I'm going to have a past,</i>

935
01:07:26,200 --> 01:07:28,885
<i>I prefer it to be multiple choice.</i>

936
01:07:30,600 --> 01:07:32,045
<i>My point</i> is...

937
01:07:33,800 --> 01:07:36,451
I went crazy.

938
01:07:37,760 --> 01:07:40,240
And I'm smart enough to admit it.

939
01:07:40,800 --> 01:07:42,529
Why Can't you?

940
01:07:44,520 --> 01:07:48,525
By clinging to reality, you're denying
